  "texts": [
    "We illustrate the mean and standard deviation of all the metrics tested with three random seeds for all the baseline methods and our approach.",
    "All the evaluation metrics are higher the better.",
    "Bold means the best, and underlined is the best runner-up for each metrics.",
    "Based on the mean and standard deviation results among three random seeds, MPA-empowered methods can significantly outperform baselines in RC and HDScore under the safety-critical scenes.",
